成为重新引进大型动物的可选之地

11
00:00:34,790 --> 00:00:36,580
I can't be sure that's a new species,
我不确定这是个新物种

12
00:00:36,697 --> 00:00:39,068
but this is the kind of thing that might be.
但很有可能是的

13
00:00:39,360 --> 00:00:44,777
This park came that close to vanishing...
这个公园几乎就要消失了

14
00:00:46,908 --> 00:00:50,257
..And I'm happy to report it is coming back.
我非常高兴地宣布它复苏了

15
00:00:50,490  --> 00:00:52,800
And this is one of the great stories.
这是一个伟大的故事

16
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:55,034
It's inspirational, I think.
我觉得真是鼓舞人心

17
00:00:55,190 --> 00:00:59,810
It's a fine, shining example of what to do with all our parks,
这是我们挽救公园的光辉案例

18
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:03,765
